               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440819-name-1168" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440819-name-1168" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440819-name-1168" type="surname" value="AYTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440819-name-1168" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM AYTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a seaman. I slept in the same room with the prisoner, on Wednesday night, the 22nd of Aug.—there were some other lodgers there—when I awoke in the morning the prisoner was gone—I missed two handkerchiefs and 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6 1/4 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>., which I had placed under my pillow when I went to bed—I have seen one of the handkerchiefs since—this is it—I gave the prisoner in charge the day following.</p>
